National Security Advisor Susan E. Rice met with the United Nations' Special Envoy for Syria Staffan de Mistura. They discussed de Mistura's efforts to achieve a freeze in Aleppo and his briefing to the UN Security Council. Rice expressed the United States' support for a political solution to Syria's civil war and measures to alleviate the suffering of the Syrian people. Rice thanked de Mistura for his renewed energy in ending the war and discussed ways the US and other partners could support his efforts.